<L>__{exterior 57th street continuous}
<A>__{patricia in the pouring rain, trying to hail a cab. she spots one across the street.}
<C>__{patricia}
<D>__{taxi! taxi! taxi!}
<A>__{she whistles a longshoreman's whistle. the cab makes a u turn, but instead of stopping for patricia it stops about twenty feet ahead for a man in an overcoat who gets into it.}
<C>__{patricia}
<D>__{excuse me what are you doing? this is my taxicab.}
<P>__{(to the driver)}
<D>__{don't take him. i am telling you right now, and i am memorizing your number, don't take him.}
<P>__{(to the man)}
<D>__{who the fuck do you think you are?}
<C>__{man in overcoat}
<D>__{are you going uptown?}
<C>__{patricia}
<D>__{yes.}
<C>__{man in overcoat}
<D>__{get in. i will drop you.}
